# 🌐 PingViz - Interactive Network Latency Dashboard

A sleek, modern web dashboard for visualizing network latency across global servers. Built with vanilla JavaScript and Chart.js, featuring real-time monitoring, animated visualizations, and a sophisticated monochrome design.

## ✨ Features

- **Real-time Latency Monitoring** - Ping 8 global server endpoints with simulated network conditions
- **Interactive Data Visualization** - Dynamic bar charts and historical line graphs
- **Smart Status Indicators** - Color-coded performance levels with pulsing animations
- **Auto-refresh Mode** - Continuous monitoring with 5-second intervals
- **High Latency Alerts** - Automatic notifications for poor network performance
- **Responsive Design** - Works seamlessly on desktop and mobile devices
- **Professional Aesthetic** - Elegant black, white, and gray theme with glassmorphic effects

## 🚀 Quick Start

1. **Clone or Download** the HTML file
2. **Open in Browser** - No build process required!
3. **Click "Ping All Servers"** to start monitoring
4. **Enable Auto-refresh** for continuous updates

## 🎯 Demo Servers

- **US East (Virginia)** - ~45ms baseline
- **US West (California)** - ~85ms baseline  
- **Europe (London)** - ~120ms baseline
- **Asia Pacific (Tokyo)** - ~180ms baseline
- **South America (São Paulo)** - ~200ms baseline
- **Australia (Sydney)** - ~250ms baseline
- **Canada (Central)** - ~65ms baseline
- **Asia Pacific (Singapore)** - ~160ms baseline

## 🛠️ Technology Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML5, CSS3, Vanilla JavaScript
- **Charts**: Chart.js v3.9.1
- **Animations**: CSS transforms and keyframes
- **Design**: Glassmorphic UI with backdrop filters
- **Responsive**: CSS Grid and Flexbox

## 📊 Performance Metrics

- **Excellent**: < 50ms (White indicators)
- **Good**: 50-99ms (Light gray indicators)  
- **Fair**: 100-199ms (Medium gray indicators)
- **Poor**: 200ms+ (Dark gray indicators)

## 🔧 Customization

**Add New Servers:**
```javascript
const servers = [
    { name: 'Custom Server', location: 'custom-1', flag: '🏴', baseLatency: 75 },
    // ... existing servers
];
```

**Modify Alert Threshold:**
```javascript
if (result.latency > 200) { // Change threshold here
    showAlert(`High latency detected: ${result.name} (${result.latency}ms)`);
}
```

## 📱 Browser Support

- ✅ Chrome/Edge (recommended)
- ✅ Firefox  
- ✅ Safari
- ✅ Mobile browsers

## 🎨 Design Philosophy

PingViz combines network engineering concepts with modern web design, creating a professional tool that showcases both technical knowledge and frontend development skills. The monochrome aesthetic provides a clean, enterprise-grade appearance suitable for network operations centers.

